---
source: tests/test_edit.rs
expression: "normalize_output(&output, temp_dir.path(), &date)"
---
$ govctl rfc new Test RFC
Created RFC: gov/rfc/RFC-0001/rfc.toml
  Clauses dir: gov/rfc/RFC-0001/clauses
exit: 0

$ govctl rfc add RFC-0001 owners @owner1
Added '@owner1' to RFC-0001.owners
exit: 0

$ govctl rfc add RFC-0001 owners @owner2
Added '@owner2' to RFC-0001.owners
exit: 0

$ govctl rfc remove RFC-0001 owners @owner1
Removed '@owner1' from RFC-0001.owners
exit: 0

$ govctl rfc get RFC-0001 owners
@test-user, @owner2
exit: 0
